{"tid":1554994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來東方記者手上有時光機 唔怪得出新聞咁快⋯","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T02:37:46.000Z","uid":78635,"like":122,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7845da7c388315914b33b1b4afe2a7e602e233e4","tid":1554994,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"7號果日已經知道9號下午4時53分有女子自殺<br />\n原來有時光機 唔怪得出新聞咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907203651765-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190907%2Fbkn-20190907203651765-0907_00822_001.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=29f7d6dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907203651765-0907_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9f9d121b89be26fbeefcb439f67d46f35f15970d","tid":1554994,"uid":78635,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"將軍澳酒店女住客吊頸亡　職員揭發報警<br />\n09月07日(六) 20:36<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳酒店揭發女子自殺案。今(9日)下午4時53分，唐德街3號一酒店職員，發現一名女客人未按時退房，於是到房間查看。惟拍門良久無人應門，用後備匙開門進入房間，赫見該姓林(58歲)女客用尼龍繩在洗手間內上吊，慌忙致電報警。消防員接報到場將女事主解下，證實她已氣絕身亡。警方在現場未檢獲遺書，初步調查相信案件無可疑，正調查其尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626"},{"pid":"03dea7e39d3bf8bd68b0c062a799a689673c0da1","tid":1554994,"uid":78635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vS27z7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvS27z7v.png&h=b689c9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsroSUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsroSUa.png&h=bbf76d